{
  "stem": "14613.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is, it is remarkable that a number of our friends that, that also hid themselves as Jews did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that it was in the next few days we found out in the village about the dozen of our friends that were on the same transport that we did that were liberated.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They also did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At, at this particular peasant, just my brother and myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the other friends went to another home of a peasant, and they stayed there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a, a, a funny experience to find, suddenly, some other people that we were in the camp, living in the same little village and taking the, the food and eating day and night.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we organized ourselves into a, a band.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would go to other villages or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would just take all the food we could find and bring it in, so that we had for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was also remarkable that, after we came-- I would say-- two hours south, that we were able to think and work and do things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We, we, of course, took some clothes from all of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we did something which I think young people, foolish people, can do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were around four, six of us that were in our age, young.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The rest of them were much older.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we found an old machine gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we took the machine gun on the tree.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we climbed on the tree with the machine gun.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
